abstract: >
  CDEWS-IAFS is an independent deterministic monitoring layer that evaluates 
  the structural stability of AI-generated or human-written text in real time.
  It computes a unified stability score C(t) using entropy H(t), semantic drift D(t),
  and structural coherence SC â€” without requiring any API or GPU.
